author: bryanduxbury
msg: THRIFT-663. java: JavaBean code generator produces incorrect setter methods

This patch causes the beans option to suppress the builder-style setter methods. It also adds a new 'private-members' option that leaves the builder-style methods, but makes the actual instance variables private.

author: adrianc
msg: Added run-install-multitenant ant target to make it easier to set up the multi-tenancy demo.
Caution: this creates three databases, with each one loaded with all demo data. Be aware of disk space use and the time required to run the task.
